{"tid":2256442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全球連線啦！香港人聽日爭唔爭氣！！","createTime":"2020-10-24T11:03:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T06:37:15.000Z","uid":274317,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0eeec5e841569cacde57de348f151d6eddea44b7","tid":2256442,"uid":274317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:03:15.000Z","msg":"【國際聲援十二港人 &mdash; 墨爾本】<br />\n<br />\n2020年8月23日，十二港人於香港東南方水域被中國海警拘捕，至今仍被扣押於深圳市鹽田看守所，未能與親屬及其委派律師會見。<br />\n<br />\n送中第六十三日，中國政府繼續漠視十二港人的基本人權，強行指派「官派律師」、拒絕提供十二港人現況並剝奪港人接受治療的權利，企圖以不公正司法達到政治目的。同時，香港政府亦一而再、再而三以司法管轄權為藉口逃避十二港人問題，拒絕提供協助並推卸責任，置12港人安危於不顧。<br />\n<br />\n10月23日，我們響應「十二港人關注組」聲援行動，於墨爾本市內快閃，希望增加國際社會關注，並要求當局盡快釋放十二港人。<br />\n<br />\n#Save12HKYouths<br />\n#Boat4HK<br />\n#FreeHK<br />\n<br />\n睇相:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/VHKTSA/photos/?tab=album&amp;album_id=371436530873576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2FVHKTSA%2Fphotos%2F%3Ftab%3Dalbum%26album_id%3D371436530873576&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLBZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=41e8e773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/VHKTSA/photos/?tab=album&amp;album_id=371436530873576</a><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/vhktsa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fvhktsa&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLBZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=f1f0d7ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/vhktsa</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/vhktsa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fvhktsa&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLBZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=c85de822\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/vhktsa</a><br />\n<br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/vhktsa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fvhktsa&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLBZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=f